  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Benefits:</p><p>•        0-20% Monthly Performance Related Pay</p><p>•        2% Monthly Medical Allowance</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>•        Identify and acquire potential clients via (but not limited to) cold calls, emails, meetings, networking events, trade shows, career fairs；</p><p>•        Manage the full sales process ：needs analysis, solution pitching, negotiation, and follow-up；</p><p>•        Prepare client proposals, quotation, contracts, and other documentation；</p><p>•        Build and maintain long-term client relationships to grow accounts；</p><p>•        Conduct market research to identify new business opportunities.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>•        At least Diploma in Business, Marketing, or related fields；</p><p>•        At least 2 years’ experience in business development；</p><p>•        B2B sales experience preferred；</p><p>•        Excellent communication, negotiation, and presentation skills；</p><p>•        Self-motivated, target-driven, and able to work independently or as part of a team；</p><p>•        Confidence in engaging stakeholders across all levels, from middle management to senior decision-makers.<br /></p><p>Maxhunt Resource Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 22C1322<br />Cynthia Lai | Registration No: R25146301</p>",
